title: JOAN DURU 2012 Highlights
description:
It's so last year, we know but it still is a good watch never the less. Joan Duru-ing what he does all over the globe of ours.
In and out, up and down and all around, check this visual eye candy and we can move forward together.
From friends of yours here at Volcom Europe.

- Music -

Song: "Onward, Upward"
Artist: Crusades
Release: New Year Repeat
